oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Harold Wells Job No. 36877
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Cooper, Stoney, 1918-1977; Ritter, Tex; Bowman, Don, 1937-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1419) for an order placed by Harold Wells for 2 orders of 50 two color window cards for a performance by Wilma Lee and Stoney Cooper at Brown Derby Lounge in Thornton, Illinois on June 10 and Tex Ritter at Brown Derby Lounge in Thornton, Illinois on June 24 and a performance by Ernest Ashworth at Brown Derby Lounge in Thornton, Illinois on May 29 and Don Bowman coming soon. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
